title: X Factor 2015: Meet the 12 finalists who'll be performing at the live shows - Leigh Journal
text:
The six chairs have been stacked away, the judges' houses have been vacated and we have our live show line-up for The X Factor 2015. Mason is easily this year's most controversial contestant - he managed to get himself thrown off the show for rowing with Simon during the Six Chair Challenge.
Start the conversation, or Read more at Leigh Journal.
